## Africana Studies Relation

**Africana Studies Relation:**  
William L. Patterson’s work embodies the intersection of racial and economic justice, making him a key figure in Africana Studies. His activism connects African-American struggles with global anti-colonial movements and offers insights into the ways systemic racism functions within capitalist societies.

